OL,4,CVue cinema chain fined #750,000 over
OL,5,Cseat crush death
OL,6, The Vue cinema chain has been fined
OL,7, #750,000 for safety breaches which led
OL,8, to the death of a man who became
OL,9, trapped under a chair.
OL,11,FIt was also ordered to pay #130,000 in
OL,12,Fcosts for what Judge Heidi Kubik QC
OL,13,Fsaid was "an accident that never should
OL,14,Fhave happened".
OL,16,FAteeq Rafiq died in March 2018 after he
OL,17,Fwas crushed by a motorised footrest at
OL,18,FBirmingham's Star City cinema.
OL,20,FThe judge said there had been a
OL,21,F"complete lack of a risk assessment".
